STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Cross-Respondent,
v.
Quashawn K. JONES, Defendant-Cross-Petitioner. C-742 September Term 2018
081862 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 27, 2019

ORDER

A cross-petition for certification of the judgment in A-000215-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the cross-petition for certification is denied.
